snippet.title: Relive Your Life Walkthrough (All Endings)
snippet.description:
This is a walkthrough of the game "Relive Your Life".

Play the game here: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/595912

You can visit my Patreon page if you want or something:
https://www.patreon.com/awalkthroughlife

Game created by FrozenFire:
Voice acting - Arin Hanson (Egoraptor)
___________
Game description (from creator):
Make sure your flash screen is active for the minigames, click the screen.

Animated and coded in 24 days, this was my final project for my studio course. Start off as a sperm cell, and play through a series of seamlessly integrated mini-games that change the course of your life. There are 29 different endings!
___________
#ReliveYourLife #walkthrough
